sdoDetails.sdoRightToAskCourt:
As the direction has been made without a hearing, you may ask the court to reconsider this order. You must do that within 7 days of receiving this order by writing to the court(and notifying any other party) and asking the court to reconsider.

Alternatively, the court may reconsider the directions at the first hearing.
